document.discussion_title: Nathan Jones had a unique nickname on the set of 'A Flying Jatt'
document.topic_text: Australian powerlifting champion-turned-actor Nathan Jones (of Mad Max: Fury Road fame), who makes his Bollywood debut in ' A Flying Jatt ', plays the demonic supervillain named Raka. »
